2
00:00:11,269 --> 00:00:12,854
Sta si mislila da radis sa ovim?

3
00:00:14,855 --> 00:00:15,731
Nista.

4
00:00:15,898 --> 00:00:19,067
Nista? Tek tako.
Od kad, Sole...!

5
00:00:19,234 --> 00:00:20,985
Raimunda,
nemoj pogresno da me shvatis.

6
00:00:21,652 --> 00:00:22,945
Nisam ja donela kofer.

7
00:00:23,237 --> 00:00:25,531
A nisi?
Koga jos ima ovde?

8
00:00:27,824 --> 00:00:30,618
Kada sam izasla iz tetkine kuce...

9
00:00:31,953 --> 00:00:32,703
Sta?

10
00:00:35,247 --> 00:00:37,123
Sta god da mi kazes,
ne verujem ti.

11
00:00:38,416 --> 00:00:40,877
Pokrasti od tetke jedino
vredno sto je imala

12
00:00:41,043 --> 00:00:44,004
i to pred njom mrtvom...
Kakva si bestidnica!

13
00:00:47,465 --> 00:00:49,217
Raimunda, nemoj da ides.

