16
00:01:23,370 --> 00:01:25,663
Sto ne popravimo ovaj ovde?

17
00:01:26,914 --> 00:01:28,374
Ne moze da se popravi.

18
00:01:30,250 --> 00:01:32,085
Otisao mu je motor.

19
00:01:32,878 --> 00:01:35,421
Rekla sam ti da ne sme niko
da udje. Ni ti.

20
00:01:35,630 --> 00:01:38,215
Videla sam da su vrata otvorena
pa sam usla uzmem cekic.

21
00:01:39,133 --> 00:01:40,467
Je li ulazio jos neko?

22
00:01:41,009 --> 00:01:42,177
Ne verujem.

23
00:01:48,349 --> 00:01:50,392
Mama, rekla si mi da si ga
se otarasila.

24
00:01:50,726 --> 00:01:52,227
Nisam mogla, Paula.

25
00:01:53,019 --> 00:01:55,605
Mislis da ja volim sto je
on tu unutra?

26
00:01:59,691 --> 00:02:03,528
Paula! Spremaj se,
za pola sata ce poceti da dolaze gosti.

27
00:02:07,948 --> 00:02:08,991
Paula!

28
00:02:12,327 --> 00:02:14,620
Sta je?
Ceo dan si takva?

29
00:02:15,037 --> 00:02:16,497
Nisam raspolozena za
proslavu.

30
00:02:16,663 --> 00:02:18,749
Nisam ni ja,
ali to je posao.

31
00:02:20,083 --> 00:02:21,584
Hajde, nemoj da si lenja.

32
00:02:22,085 --> 00:02:24,253
Hajde, duso,
ja cu ti pomoci.

33
00:02:26,046 --> 00:02:27,214
Sta ti je?

34
00:02:27,589 --> 00:02:31,384
Ne mogu da izbacim iz glave
da je on tamo u onom spajzu.

35
00:02:32,677 --> 00:02:35,971
To je najbolji nacin da poludis
a i ja zajedno sa tobom.

36
00:02:36,138 --> 00:02:39,099
Mama, ti ne znas kakav je osecaj
kad znas da si ubila svoga oca.

37
00:02:40,350 --> 00:02:42,143
Pako nije bio tvoj otac.

38
00:02:43,561 --> 00:02:45,229
Nemoj me lagati vise.

39
00:02:45,354 --> 00:02:48,648
Znam da to radis zbog mene,
ali nemoj me lagati vise.

40
00:02:48,815 --> 00:02:49,941
Ne lazem te.

41
00:02:50,733 --> 00:02:52,568
Pako te je priznao kao cerku,

42
00:02:52,818 --> 00:02:55,445
ali znaj da ti on nije bioloski otac.

43
00:03:00,408 --> 00:03:02,243
Hoces li mi onda reci istinu?

44
00:03:02,660 --> 00:03:05,954
Da. Ali to ne opravdava ono
sto je uradio.

45
00:03:10,041 --> 00:03:13,210
Paula, obecavam da cu ti
sve ispricati neki drugi put.

46
00:03:14,086 --> 00:03:17,005
Hajdemo da se spremamo.
Sta dobijamo ako ostanemo ovde?

47
00:03:17,755 --> 00:03:19,257
Ko je moj otac?

48
00:03:21,008 --> 00:03:22,050
Jedan iz sela.

49
00:03:22,217 --> 00:03:23,301
Jel ga poznajem?

50
00:03:25,387 --> 00:03:26,679
Umro je.

51
00:03:28,431 --> 00:03:32,100
Paula, kunem ti se da cu ti
sve ispricati. Kunem ti se.

52
00:03:33,101 --> 00:03:34,561
Obecavas?

53
00:03:45,653 --> 00:03:48,239
-Dva mohita.
-Dva mohita ovde, stizu!

54
00:03:48,697 --> 00:03:51,199
Sta zelis srce?
Isto dva mohita?

55
00:03:51,741 --> 00:03:54,369
Ne, hocu onaj sa limunom,
taj je odlican.

56
00:04:00,415 --> 00:04:02,375
Treba nam jos casa.

57
00:04:02,500 --> 00:04:03,876
Ne mogu da postignem.

58
00:04:04,210 --> 00:04:05,795
Jel si videla kako mi je lepa
Paula?

59
00:04:07,129 --> 00:04:08,672
Jebem ti!

60
00:04:11,091 --> 00:04:11,966
Uzmi.

61
00:04:12,634 --> 00:04:13,926
Hvala.

62
00:04:17,012 --> 00:04:18,305
Ah, sto je jak!

63
00:04:18,472 --> 00:04:20,348
Ne mogu vise da pijem,
odlicni su!

64
00:04:20,515 --> 00:04:24,226
Slusaj, sa tvojim dekolteom
i mojim mohitima, mozemo pare da namlatimo.

65
00:04:24,393 --> 00:04:27,521
Zasto ne bismo radile nocu, da vidimo
da li ce da zazivi

66
00:04:27,688 --> 00:04:28,980
ovaj sumorni kraj.

67
00:04:29,147 --> 00:04:30,899
Videcemo,
najbitnije je

68
00:04:31,065 --> 00:04:33,484
da su zadovoljni veceras.
Uzmi. Mohito!

69
00:04:34,610 --> 00:04:36,403
Lezi dole da te ne vide.

70
00:04:36,570 --> 00:04:39,239
Zazelela sam se Raimunde i
devojcice.

71
00:04:40,198 --> 00:04:42,283
Onaj dan sam im samo noge videla.

72
00:04:42,450 --> 00:04:44,160
I vidi sta si izazvala!

73
00:04:45,244 --> 00:04:46,495
Jel ovo taj restoran?

74
00:04:48,496 --> 00:04:51,749
Rekla mi je da joj ide dobro,
ali nisam ovako zamisljala.

75
00:04:52,083 --> 00:04:53,417
I zasluzila je.

76
00:04:53,584 --> 00:04:55,460
Jadnica, toliko je toga prezivela.

77
00:05:04,968 --> 00:05:07,429
Ne izlazi iz auta,
i sagni se da te ne vide!

78
00:05:07,595 --> 00:05:09,013
Odavde ne vidim nikoga!

79
00:05:39,413 --> 00:05:42,499
Otkud ti ovde?
Drago mi je da si dosla!

80
00:05:42,666 --> 00:05:46,711
Donela sam ti tetka Pauline stvari.
Nisam znala da imas proslavu.

81
00:05:46,878 --> 00:05:49,171
Neka filmska ekipa slavi
zavrsetak snimanja.

82
00:05:49,338 --> 00:05:51,465
Ja sam im spremala hranu
ovih dana.

83
00:05:51,632 --> 00:05:55,051
-Hajde da prebacimo kofer.
- Zasto si uznemirena?

84
00:05:55,218 --> 00:05:56,636
Nikad mi se tako nesto nije desilo

85
00:05:56,761 --> 00:05:59,513
da pokupim tetkine stvari,
i jos da ih sakrijem.

86
00:05:59,638 --> 00:06:01,306
Znam, izvini zbog onog
sto sam ti rekla,

87
00:06:01,473 --> 00:06:03,683
ali znas ti mene,
pukla sam...pukla!

88
00:06:03,850 --> 00:06:04,601
Cao, tetka.

89
00:06:04,767 --> 00:06:05,476
Cao.

90
00:06:06,727 --> 00:06:07,978
Hoces nesto da popijes?

91
00:06:08,145 --> 00:06:09,188
Ne.

92
00:06:36,293 --> 00:06:37,419
Secas se?

93
00:06:37,878 --> 00:06:39,629
Kako da se ne secam?

94
00:06:39,921 --> 00:06:42,215
Koliko dugo nisam
cula kako pevas!

95
00:06:42,673 --> 00:06:44,758
Pa ja je nikad nisam cula
kako peva.

96
00:06:47,052 --> 00:06:48,220
Stvarno?

97
00:06:48,386 --> 00:06:49,721
Stvarno, mama, nikad!

98
00:06:51,848 --> 00:06:53,349
Jel ti se svidja, duso?

99
00:06:53,474 --> 00:06:55,392
S obzirom na situaciju,
naravno!

100
00:07:00,980 --> 00:07:02,023
Gledaj sad.

101
00:07:06,026 --> 00:07:07,194
Ne mogu da verujem.

102
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,328
Gde da stanem?

103
00:07:18,494 --> 00:07:19,203
Evo ovde.

104
00:07:25,500 --> 00:07:28,628
Narode!
Sedite, ova zena ce vam sada pevati.

105
00:07:33,173 --> 00:07:34,341
Dobro vece.

106
00:07:35,342 --> 00:07:37,135
Zelela bih da se zahvalim ekipi

107
00:07:37,302 --> 00:07:39,637
zbog posla koji su mi dali da radim
ovih nedelja.

108
00:07:40,387 --> 00:07:42,139
Hvala vam puno, od srca.

109
00:07:42,764 --> 00:07:44,808
Proslo je dosta vremena od kad
nisam pevala, bas dosta,

110
00:07:45,517 --> 00:07:47,602
ali sada cu otpevati nesto,
pa da vidimo kako zvuci.

111
00:08:12,789 --> 00:08:14,999
Ovu pesmu ju je tvoja baka
naucila

112
00:08:15,166 --> 00:08:17,460
za izvodjenje na izboru
za decu pevace.

113
00:09:28,393 --> 00:09:29,352
Bravo!

114
00:10:00,085 --> 00:10:01,378
Autos Amigo,izvolite?

115
00:10:02,170 --> 00:10:04,964
Halo, dobar dan.
Javljam se povodom oglasa...

116
00:10:05,215 --> 00:10:07,758
htela bih da iznajmim kombi.

117
00:10:08,134 --> 00:10:10,135
Koji tip, i na koje vreme?

118
00:10:10,302 --> 00:10:13,471
Pa neki obicni,
najjeftiniji koji imate, na jedan dan.

119
00:10:18,267 --> 00:10:19,143
Da?

120
00:10:19,518 --> 00:10:21,561
Mogu li da razgovaram sa gospodjom
Raimundom?

121
00:10:22,270 --> 00:10:23,188
Da, ja sam.

122
00:10:23,646 --> 00:10:27,400
Gdin Emilio mi je ostavio vas telefon,
hteo bih da pogledam restoran.

123
00:10:27,566 --> 00:10:30,277
Recite mi kada mogu da ga pogledam.
Ja sam Karlos.

124
00:10:31,444 --> 00:10:32,529
Pa...

125
00:10:33,238 --> 00:10:35,406
moracu da vam se javim kasnije,

126
00:10:35,573 --> 00:10:38,450
zato sto ga je ostavio jednom komsiji.

127
00:10:38,909 --> 00:10:40,994
Ali, gdin Emilio mi nije
nista rekao.

128
00:10:41,870 --> 00:10:44,288
Naravno, gdin Emilio ima
svoju strategiju, za svaki slucaj.

129
00:10:44,455 --> 00:10:47,333
Mogu li da razgovaram sa osobom,
koja ima kljuc od restorana?

130
00:10:47,624 --> 00:10:49,793
Ali on trenutno nije tu,
zao mi je.

131
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:53,337
Ali, nazovite vi gdin-a Emilija
on ce vam sve objasniti.

132
00:10:54,046 --> 00:10:55,047
Dobro, hvala.

133
00:10:56,465 --> 00:10:57,508
Do vidjenja.

134
00:11:08,475 --> 00:11:09,267
Da recite?

135
00:11:09,434 --> 00:11:11,394
Emilio,
ovde Raimunda.

136
00:11:11,561 --> 00:11:14,939
Drago mi je da te cujem!
Jel bio neko da pogleda restoran?

137
00:11:15,064 --> 00:11:18,817
Da, ali nije ostavio dobar utisak.
Verujem da je hteo da koristi restoran kao paravan.

138
00:11:18,983 --> 00:11:20,318
Kao paravan? Za sta?

139
00:11:20,485 --> 00:11:23,404
Pa za drogu, ili da otvori
javnu kucu...ne znam.

140
00:11:23,571 --> 00:11:27,240
Kada sam mu pomenula da posao
nije isao, rekao je: "jos bolje!"

141
00:11:27,407 --> 00:11:29,534
Zasto si mu to rekla, zeno?

142
00:11:31,244 --> 00:11:33,662
Ah, Emilio, htela sam da te zovem
ovih dana,

143
00:11:34,246 --> 00:11:35,789
i nadam se da ces me razumeti.

144
00:11:36,498 --> 00:11:38,833
Znam da nije trebalo ovo da se desi,
ali...

145
00:11:40,835 --> 00:11:43,003
ja sam nastavila da radim u restoranu.

146
00:11:43,170 --> 00:11:44,671
Molim?Sta hoces da kazes?

147
00:11:46,464 --> 00:11:48,508
Daj mi 5 minuta da ti objasnim.

148
00:11:48,841 --> 00:11:51,343
Daleko si otisla, Raimunda,
daleko.

149
00:11:51,510 --> 00:11:52,511
Jesam.

150
00:11:52,678 --> 00:11:54,429
Iskoristila si moje
poverenje.

151
00:11:55,472 --> 00:11:58,433
Znam da nije opravdanje,
ali kada je naisla ova filmska ekipa

152
00:11:58,599 --> 00:12:02,311
bila sam ocajna.
I sada kad nas je Pako napustio...

153
00:12:02,478 --> 00:12:03,687
Sta?Pako te je ostavio?

154
00:12:04,187 --> 00:12:06,898
Da. Posvadjali smo se...

155
00:12:07,190 --> 00:12:09,567
on je otisao,
i ne verujem da ce se vratiti.

156
00:12:09,692 --> 00:12:12,319
Otisao je istog dana kad i ti
u Barselonu.

157
00:12:13,153 --> 00:12:14,696
Kako si to podnela?

158
00:12:14,863 --> 00:12:19,325
Ja? Tesko, video si me.
Hvatam se za slamku spasa.

159
00:12:19,491 --> 00:12:22,327
Dobro, ajde da vidimo
kako da se dogovorimo.

160
00:12:23,662 --> 00:12:28,165
Reci mi koliko treba da ti placam mesecno
samo mi daj malo vremena.

161
00:12:48,348 --> 00:12:48,974
Da?

162
00:12:49,141 --> 00:12:50,308
Raimunda?

163
00:12:50,725 --> 00:12:52,018
Da, ko je to?

164
00:12:52,185 --> 00:12:55,313
Ovde Agustina.
Ja sam u Madridu, i htela bih da te vidim.

165
00:12:56,981 --> 00:12:59,775
Agustina, u guzvi sam.
Imam mnogo obaveza.

166
00:12:59,983 --> 00:13:00,859
A sutra?

167
00:13:01,026 --> 00:13:03,611
Ne mogu ni sutra.
Cela ova nedelja mi je zauzeta.

168
00:13:03,778 --> 00:13:06,739
Ne govori mi to.
Ja sam u bolnici.

169
00:13:07,072 --> 00:13:08,323
Sta ti se desilo?

170
00:13:08,490 --> 00:13:11,451
Imam rak.
Juce su mi rekli doktori.

171
00:13:11,618 --> 00:13:13,286
Moram da te vidim.

172
00:13:14,495 --> 00:13:17,080
Reci mi u kojoj si bolnici,
odmah dolazim.

173
00:13:17,206 --> 00:13:18,623
U centralnoj bolnici.

174
00:13:19,582 --> 00:13:21,918
Bog ce ti platiti, Raimunda.

175
00:13:25,212 --> 00:13:26,547
Hvala.

176
00:13:27,798 --> 00:13:30,591
Idi ti, ja zurim.
Daj ovo tetki.

177
00:13:37,556 --> 00:13:38,306
Zdravo, tetka.

178
00:13:38,473 --> 00:13:39,641
Otkud ti ovde?

179
00:13:40,058 --> 00:13:41,392
Sole!

180
00:13:41,559 --> 00:13:42,685
Sole!

181
00:13:43,269 --> 00:13:44,686
To se tvoja majka dere.

182
00:13:45,395 --> 00:13:47,105
Sole, izadji na prozor!

183
00:13:49,816 --> 00:13:50,525
Sta je bilo?

184
00:13:50,733 --> 00:13:52,067
Ostavila sam ti Paulu!

185
00:13:52,234 --> 00:13:53,861
Ali, Raimunda, imam posla.

186
00:13:54,027 --> 00:13:57,489
Moram da idem do bolnice.
Agustina ima rak.

187
00:13:57,655 --> 00:13:59,615
Ma sta kazes?Jadnica!

188
00:13:59,782 --> 00:14:02,910
Dala sam devojcici tetkinu torbu,
uzmi je ti.

189
00:14:03,076 --> 00:14:06,329
Idem nesto da zavrsim,
vraticu se brzo.

190
00:14:06,579 --> 00:14:09,790
Pozdravi Agustinu.
Reci joj da cu doci da je posetim.

191
00:14:09,957 --> 00:14:11,333
Hocu.

192
00:14:14,377 --> 00:14:16,004
Jel mogu da udjem, tetka?

193
00:14:17,672 --> 00:14:18,923
Da, duso, udji.

194
00:14:39,064 --> 00:14:40,107
Kako si, mila?

195
00:14:43,693 --> 00:14:45,820
Otvorili su me i zatvorili.

196
00:14:46,487 --> 00:14:48,072
Znala sam da je nesto lose.

197
00:14:48,239 --> 00:14:50,115
Ne gubi nadu, zeno!

198
00:14:51,825 --> 00:14:53,535
Bas je lepo cvece!

199
00:14:54,327 --> 00:14:57,454
Nisi morala da se trosis.
Stavi ga ovde.

200
00:15:01,374 --> 00:15:02,333
Raimunda,

201
00:15:04,127 --> 00:15:05,878
moram da te zamolim za uslugu.

202
00:15:06,212 --> 00:15:08,046
Samo reci Agustina.

203
00:15:08,797 --> 00:15:10,090
Zatvori vrata.

204
00:15:14,343 --> 00:15:15,511
Uzmi stolicu.

205
00:15:26,395 --> 00:15:27,979
Nije mi jos mnogo ostalo,

206
00:15:29,272 --> 00:15:32,441
ali ne zelim da umrem dok ne saznam
sta se desilo sa mojom majkom.

207
00:15:34,110 --> 00:15:35,694
Sta ja mogu da uradim?

208
00:15:36,570 --> 00:15:39,864
Mozes mi reci je li ziva ili mrtva.

209
00:15:41,365 --> 00:15:42,533
Kako ja to mogu da znam?

210
00:15:43,200 --> 00:15:44,535
Pitaj svoju majku.

211
00:15:46,328 --> 00:15:48,955
Moju majku?
Ali ona je mrtva, Agustina!

212
00:15:49,247 --> 00:15:52,416
Jeste, ali se pojavila kod tvoje
tetke Paule,

213
00:15:52,666 --> 00:15:55,877
i brinula se o njoj dok nije umrla.
To zna celo selo.

214
00:15:56,711 --> 00:16:00,173
Ako se pojavi kod vas,
pitaj je za moju majku.

215
00:16:00,881 --> 00:16:02,508
Samo te to molim.

216
00:16:02,675 --> 00:16:06,303
Agustina, trazis od mene nemoguce.
Jesi li ti videla nju

217
00:16:06,469 --> 00:16:07,679
svojim ocima?

218
00:16:08,471 --> 00:16:09,222
Ne.

219
00:16:09,388 --> 00:16:11,307
Pa kad je ti nisi videla, koja zivis
preko puta...

220
00:16:12,016 --> 00:16:13,767
Mislim da me je izbegavala,
vidi.

221
00:16:14,518 --> 00:16:17,562
Ali sam hiljadu puta cula tvoju tetku
kako prica sa njom.

222
00:16:19,397 --> 00:16:22,524
Vidi, ako saznam nesto,
budi sigurna da cu ti reci.

223
00:16:24,651 --> 00:16:26,277
Samo cini mi se da je to malo nemoguce.

224
00:16:29,447 --> 00:16:31,198
Dugujes mi, Raimunda.

225
00:16:32,407 --> 00:16:33,742
Samo te molim za tu uslugu.

226
00:16:33,909 --> 00:16:36,703
Idem ja, moram mnogo toga da
obavim danas.

227
00:16:36,869 --> 00:16:40,080
Cekaj, moja sestra hoce da razgovara
sa tobom, samo sto nije stigla.

228
00:16:40,247 --> 00:16:42,916
Drugi put.
Sad stvarno zurim.

229
00:16:43,083 --> 00:16:45,376
Hoce nesto u vezi televizije da
te pita.

230
00:16:45,710 --> 00:16:48,879
Znas da ona vodi emisiju
"Gde su, sta rade?"

231
00:16:49,213 --> 00:16:51,465
Ima jedno iznenadjenje za tebe,
setila se,

232
00:16:51,631 --> 00:16:55,468
kad ste bile klinke, i kad
ste isle na kasting,

233
00:16:56,052 --> 00:16:58,304
i pojavile se u 3-4 emisija

234
00:16:58,470 --> 00:17:00,514
sa intervjuima, muzikom i pesmama

235
00:17:00,639 --> 00:17:03,892
za sva vremena.

236
00:17:04,058 --> 00:17:06,811
Reci tvojoj sestri da ja
ne volim televiziju.

237
00:17:07,102 --> 00:17:10,230
Ne volim je ni ja. Reci cu joj.
Ali nemoj da zaboravis sta sam ti rekla.

238
00:17:10,772 --> 00:17:11,773
Ok.

239
00:17:14,484 --> 00:17:17,152
Kol'ko vidim, ruskinja bas voli
da gleda televiziju.

240
00:17:18,070 --> 00:17:21,156
Ne znam koliko moze da razume,
ali kao da je hipnotise.

241
00:17:21,656 --> 00:17:23,866
Mora da ima nesto u tom
djubretu od televizije.

242
00:17:24,075 --> 00:17:27,453
Ja kad zasednem ispred TV-a,
ne znam da ustanem.

243
00:17:27,619 --> 00:17:30,830
Svaki put se sve vise zgrazavam,
ali ne mogu da ustanem.

244
00:17:30,955 --> 00:17:32,373
Za mene je to kao droga.

245
00:17:32,540 --> 00:17:36,502
Sinoc nisam gledala do kasno,
zaspala sam k'o zaklana.

246
00:17:36,668 --> 00:17:38,753
Od tolike buke,
mozes da poludis.

247
00:17:41,047 --> 00:17:42,423
Svidjaju ti se lutke?

248
00:17:42,798 --> 00:17:46,093
Ova da, lici mi na neku iz
filmova o teroristima.

249
00:17:46,260 --> 00:17:47,677
Te su mnogo stare.

250
00:17:47,844 --> 00:17:51,347
Tvoja mama se igrala sa njima
dok je bila trudna sa tobom.

251
00:17:51,514 --> 00:17:53,099
Zasto nije zivela sa tobom?

252
00:17:54,308 --> 00:17:56,310
Nismo bili bas pri parama.

253
00:17:56,810 --> 00:17:59,104
Tvoj deda je otisao da radi
u Venecuelu

254
00:17:59,270 --> 00:18:00,938
a ja sam ostala sa Sole,

255
00:18:01,647 --> 00:18:04,316
a tvoja mama je otisla da zivi
sa tetka Paulom.

256
00:18:05,234 --> 00:18:06,568
Sta ti je ona pricala?

257
00:18:06,735 --> 00:18:09,862
Nista, ne voli da prica
o tom vremenu.

258
00:18:10,613 --> 00:18:12,031
Jel se dobro slazete?

259
00:18:12,198 --> 00:18:13,615
Sada bolje.

260
00:18:13,782 --> 00:18:16,034
Ali ponekad je mnogo nervozna,
bako.

261
00:18:16,201 --> 00:18:17,368
Ima jak karakter.

262
00:18:17,911 --> 00:18:19,745
Kako si se ti slagala
sa njom?

263
00:18:20,246 --> 00:18:22,873
Kao mala, bila je zlatno dete,

264
00:18:23,707 --> 00:18:25,875
ali kad je usla u adolescentsko
doba,

265
00:18:26,835 --> 00:18:28,878
iz meni nepoznatih razloga,

266
00:18:30,004 --> 00:18:31,714
se odvojila od mene.

267
00:18:33,173 --> 00:18:35,133
a posle sam je skroz izgubila.

268
00:18:36,926 --> 00:18:38,594
Tvoja mama me nije volela.

269
00:18:40,804 --> 00:18:44,307
Mnogo boli kad
cerka ne voli majku.

270
00:18:46,476 --> 00:18:50,062
Zato, sad kad ste ostale same,

271
00:18:50,479 --> 00:18:52,272
moras je puno voleti,

272
00:18:52,689 --> 00:18:54,357
da ona to oseti.

273
00:18:55,191 --> 00:18:57,151
Zasto si se pojavila, bako?

274
00:18:59,903 --> 00:19:01,738
Zato sto sam bila
jako usamljena.

275
00:19:05,450 --> 00:19:06,367
Dobar dan.

276
00:19:06,867 --> 00:19:07,743
Zdravo.

277
00:19:08,327 --> 00:19:11,371
Dacete mi 8 metara plasticnog
konopca.

278
00:19:11,538 --> 00:19:12,914
I lepljivu traku.

279
00:19:13,081 --> 00:19:14,207
Koliko traka?

280
00:19:14,499 --> 00:19:15,917
4-5 rolni.

281
00:19:16,083 --> 00:19:17,126
Odlicno.

282
00:19:17,960 --> 00:19:19,169
Evo 5 komada.

283
00:19:23,589 --> 00:19:24,257
Jedan,

284
00:19:25,049 --> 00:19:25,633
Dva...

285
00:19:26,050 --> 00:19:28,302
Ah, i kramp i asov.

286
00:19:28,802 --> 00:19:29,761
Odlicno.

287
00:20:04,206 --> 00:20:05,457
Do vidjenja, Sole.

288
00:20:05,624 --> 00:20:06,958
Hvala vam.

289
00:20:07,417 --> 00:20:08,501
Zdravo. Ovo joj je sestra.

290
00:20:08,668 --> 00:20:10,461
Kako si RAIMUNDA?

291
00:20:10,962 --> 00:20:11,837
Premoreno.

292
00:20:12,004 --> 00:20:13,088
Kako je Agustina?

293
00:20:13,464 --> 00:20:14,882
Luda ko koza.

294
00:20:15,048 --> 00:20:15,799
Cao, mama!

295
00:20:16,967 --> 00:20:18,343
Sta ti je?

296
00:20:18,510 --> 00:20:19,510
Nista.

297
00:20:20,011 --> 00:20:22,012
Duso, donesi mi casu vode.

298
00:20:22,555 --> 00:20:25,223
Jel ti nije problem da ostane
veceras kod tebe?

299
00:20:25,390 --> 00:20:27,142
Ne, ali gde da spava?

300
00:20:27,517 --> 00:20:28,810
Pa u sobi.

301
00:20:30,353 --> 00:20:33,397
Pako ce doci veceras kuci.
Moramo da razgovaramo,

302
00:20:33,814 --> 00:20:35,232
i htela bih da budem sama.

303
00:20:36,191 --> 00:20:37,066
Dobro.

304
00:20:38,651 --> 00:20:41,111
Veceras ces spavati ovde.

305
00:20:45,615 --> 00:20:48,993
Dobro, idem ja,
kakva me luda noc ocekuje.

306
00:21:18,892 --> 00:21:20,060
Zdravo!

307
00:21:20,227 --> 00:21:21,103
Hej, gde si?

308
00:21:21,269 --> 00:21:23,354
Moram da te zamolim za
uslugu, veceras.

309
00:21:23,521 --> 00:21:25,606
Veceras, zar ne moze da
saceka do sutra?

310
00:21:25,773 --> 00:21:28,233
Ne. Ali platicu ti,
kao i svaka musterija.

311
00:21:28,484 --> 00:21:30,861
Ne ljubavi,
tebi cu da dam za dzabe.

312
00:21:31,444 --> 00:21:34,530
Ribo, nisam znala da si
takva.

313
00:21:34,697 --> 00:21:35,656
Ma ne to.

314
00:21:35,906 --> 00:21:39,659
Ne? Pa ako nije za hopa-cupa,
za sta me onda pitas?

315
00:21:39,910 --> 00:21:41,411
Objasnicu ti u kombiju.

316
00:21:41,578 --> 00:21:44,163
Moras da mi pomognes da ubacim
zamrzivac u kombi.

317
00:21:44,330 --> 00:21:45,915
Nosim ga na otpad.

318
00:21:46,081 --> 00:21:48,166
Necemo moci nas dve
da ga ubacimo.

319
00:21:48,333 --> 00:21:50,377
Trazicemo od komsiluka da nam
pomognu.

320
00:21:50,543 --> 00:21:52,795
Obuci nesto,
cekam te na terasi.

321
00:21:52,962 --> 00:21:53,713
Sta da obucem?

322
00:21:53,879 --> 00:21:55,714
Pa nesto u cemu neces
puci.

323
00:21:55,881 --> 00:21:57,924
Cekaj, cekaj malo.

324
00:21:58,091 --> 00:21:59,301
Cekaj ovde je stepenik!

325
00:21:59,467 --> 00:22:00,552
Jel drzimo?

326
00:22:00,718 --> 00:22:02,386
Jel moze.
Ne moze.

327
00:22:02,553 --> 00:22:05,723
Ne moze, zeno.
Sad moze.

328
00:22:05,889 --> 00:22:07,015
Hajdete sad vi.

329
00:22:09,809 --> 00:22:11,936
Sad moramo da ga podignemo.

330
00:22:12,103 --> 00:22:14,355
Hajde! Jedan, dva, tri!

331
00:22:17,983 --> 00:22:20,193
Idemo, na tri!
Jedan, dva, tri!

332
00:22:20,360 --> 00:22:21,152
Tri!

333
00:22:21,319 --> 00:22:22,361
Guraj.

334
00:22:23,070 --> 00:22:24,113
Ah!

335
00:22:24,613 --> 00:22:25,906
Ugurasmo ga.

336
00:22:26,740 --> 00:22:28,241
Zamalo da se userem!

337
00:22:28,408 --> 00:22:29,867
Jesi li se povredila?

338
00:22:30,034 --> 00:22:33,203
Ne. Slezina samo sto
mi nije pukla.

339
00:22:33,954 --> 00:22:34,913
Hajde.

340
00:22:35,831 --> 00:22:37,123
Gde idemo?

341
00:22:38,208 --> 00:22:39,750
Idemo do reke Hukar.

342
00:22:39,917 --> 00:22:41,252
Gde je to?

343
00:22:42,086 --> 00:22:43,629
Oko 180 km.

344
00:22:43,795 --> 00:22:47,590
180 km? Pa dok
stignemo i dok se vratimo, vec ce da svane.

345
00:22:47,757 --> 00:22:49,425
Rekla sam ti da cu ti
platiti na sat.

346
00:22:49,884 --> 00:22:51,177
Samo da ti pravim drustvo?

347
00:22:51,552 --> 00:22:53,970
Da mi pravis drustvo,
da iskopamo rupu.

348
00:22:54,137 --> 00:22:56,556
ubacimo zamrzivac, i
nista me ne pitaj.

349
00:22:56,931 --> 00:22:59,892
Vidi, Mundita,
zahvalna sam ti sto imas poverenja,

350
00:23:00,059 --> 00:23:02,477
ali moj zivot je vec ionako
dosta komplikovan!

351
00:23:02,644 --> 00:23:05,772
Nemam posao, ni papire,
radim na ulici da prezivim.

352
00:23:05,939 --> 00:23:07,857
Jebo te, mogla si bar da
me pitas!

353
00:23:08,024 --> 00:23:09,900
Dobro, pitam te sad,
kazi koliko?

354
00:23:10,067 --> 00:23:12,277
Trebala si da me pitas.

355
00:23:14,821 --> 00:23:15,822
Da vidimo...

356
00:23:17,406 --> 00:23:18,365
daj mi nocnu.

357
00:23:19,033 --> 00:23:20,075
Kakvu nocnu?

358
00:23:20,325 --> 00:23:22,661
Nocnu smenu u restoranu.
Na mesec dana.

359
00:23:23,203 --> 00:23:26,747
I sto zaradim na koktelima to je za mene.
A ti kupujes pice.

360
00:23:27,039 --> 00:23:30,459
Dogovoreno, drugarice.
Ali o ovome, ni reci, jel jasno?

361
00:23:31,418 --> 00:23:33,837
Jos bolje!Sad sam ti saucesnik.

362
00:23:34,837 --> 00:23:36,839
Smiri se,
nisam nikoga ubila.

363
00:23:37,006 --> 00:23:38,465
Ne, nista mi ne pricaj.

364
00:23:39,049 --> 00:23:40,759
Nisam ni mislila.

365
00:24:16,413 --> 00:24:19,124
Ajde bezi.
Bezi, bezi, bezi. Daj mi.

366
00:24:33,093 --> 00:24:34,470
Cekaj malo...

367
00:24:36,013 --> 00:24:37,180
Oh, boze!

368
00:24:39,724 --> 00:24:41,600
Ah, ne mogu vise,
mrtva sam.

369
00:24:42,226 --> 00:24:44,478
Odmori se malo,
dok ja nabacam zemlju.

370
00:25:45,570 --> 00:25:47,113
Odkud ti ovde, Agustina?

371
00:25:49,948 --> 00:25:51,158
Jel mozemo da popricamo?

372
00:25:51,324 --> 00:25:52,659
Mnogo sam zauzeta.

373
00:25:53,951 --> 00:25:55,119
Hajde, dodji ovamo.

374
00:26:01,624 --> 00:26:03,084
Kako ti je?

375
00:26:03,251 --> 00:26:05,586
Isto.
Jesi li saznala nesto?

376
00:26:05,753 --> 00:26:06,754
O cemu?

377
00:26:07,129 --> 00:26:08,755
O onome sto sam te
pitala.

378
00:26:09,631 --> 00:26:11,758
Mislila sam da ne
mislis ozbiljno.

379
00:26:13,092 --> 00:26:14,677
Nemas nista protiv
da sednem?

380
00:26:16,345 --> 00:26:18,096
Ah, Raimunda...

381
00:26:19,556 --> 00:26:21,182
razumi me.

382
00:26:21,891 --> 00:26:25,769
Uradicu sve sto hoces,
samo me ne pitaj za nemoguce.

383
00:26:25,936 --> 00:26:28,313
Samo zelim da znam da li
je ziva ili mrtva!

384
00:26:33,025 --> 00:26:36,028
Agustina,
ja razumem da od raka

385
00:26:36,194 --> 00:26:37,863
moze covek da poludi,

386
00:26:38,029 --> 00:26:40,907
ali nemas prava da nam
komplikujes zivot,

387
00:26:41,073 --> 00:26:42,825
ionako je vec isuvise komplikovan.

388
00:26:44,243 --> 00:26:46,912
Onog dana kada su tvoji roditelji
umrli u pozaru,

389
00:26:47,162 --> 00:26:49,080
moja majka je nestala.

390
00:26:53,625 --> 00:26:56,128
Ti ne vidis nikakvu
povezanost?

391
00:26:56,628 --> 00:26:58,838
Ne, to je samo koincidencija.

392
00:26:59,755 --> 00:27:02,424
Po tvojoj prici,
tvoja majka je otisla ujutru...

393
00:27:02,841 --> 00:27:05,385
i nije joj bio prvi put da
tako odlazi.

394
00:27:05,552 --> 00:27:09,222
Odgajala te je tvoja baba,
zato sto ti majka nikad nije bila kod kuce!

395
00:27:09,388 --> 00:27:11,265
Nemoj sad da me zavrces.

396
00:27:11,432 --> 00:27:13,141
Moja majka je otisla ujutru,

397
00:27:13,850 --> 00:27:16,603
ali otisla je da se nadje sa tvojim ocem
na cosku.

398
00:27:17,228 --> 00:27:19,772
To je laz.
Niko je nije video.

399
00:27:19,939 --> 00:27:23,400
Naravno,
pazila je da je niko ne vidi.

400
00:27:24,442 --> 00:27:25,443
Raimunda,

401
00:27:26,319 --> 00:27:29,905
moja majka,
je bila sa tvojim ocem.

402
00:27:30,864 --> 00:27:32,491
Ma sta pricas!

403
00:27:34,534 --> 00:27:37,411
Moja majka je obozavala mog oca!
Ona to nikad ne bi dozvolila!

404
00:27:37,578 --> 00:27:40,205
Zato ga je ostavila,
i otisla da zivi kod tetka Paule!

405
00:27:40,622 --> 00:27:43,041
Otisla je da zivi kod tetka Paule,
zato sto tetki nije bilo dobro,

406
00:27:43,208 --> 00:27:45,960
ali nikada nije ostavila mog oca.
Delile ih samo dve kuce.

407
00:27:46,085 --> 00:27:47,837
Ti ne mozes to da znas,
jer nisi bila tamo,

408
00:27:48,003 --> 00:27:51,089
i takoreci nisi imala
kontakt sa svojom majkom nekoliko godina.

409
00:27:51,256 --> 00:27:54,717
Uvek se zalila da je ne jebes ni 2%.

410
00:27:56,969 --> 00:27:58,679
Mnogo toga sam cula, Raimunda.

411
00:28:00,180 --> 00:28:04,017
Jednom prilikom sam cula
razgovor tvoje i moje majke.

412
00:28:04,600 --> 00:28:08,604
I tvoja majka je rekla da je ostavila
tvog oca, i da je nije briga za njega.

413
00:28:08,770 --> 00:28:10,355
I da nije polagala nade u njega,

414
00:28:10,522 --> 00:28:13,608
jer je tvoj otac samo
jurio za zenama.

415
00:28:16,652 --> 00:28:18,570
Sta hoces da kazes, Agustina?

416
00:28:20,113 --> 00:28:21,781
Da je smrt tvojih roditelja,

417
00:28:22,365 --> 00:28:25,201
i nestanak moje majke, povezan!

418
00:28:27,869 --> 00:28:30,455
I sto to nisi prijavila policiji?

419
00:28:30,955 --> 00:28:33,124
Zato sto policija previse ispituje

420
00:28:33,291 --> 00:28:36,418
a prljav ves moramo sami da operemo.

421
00:28:37,252 --> 00:28:40,630
Zbog toga nisam zelela da idem ni na
televiziju, uprkos insistiranju moje sestre.

422
00:28:41,464 --> 00:28:44,258
Ali ovo moramo da resimo
ti i ja izmedju sebe.

423
00:28:46,760 --> 00:28:48,928
Agustina, posao me ceka.

424
00:28:52,598 --> 00:28:54,391
Razmisli malo o ovome
sto sam ti rekla.

425
00:28:55,142 --> 00:28:56,685
Kako je Pako?

426
00:28:57,310 --> 00:28:58,228
Dobro.

427
00:28:59,229 --> 00:29:00,313
Odlicno.

428
00:29:05,734 --> 00:29:08,403
Zar ne bi trebalo da se javimo
tetki da odlazimo.

429
00:29:08,570 --> 00:29:09,946
Ona ne mrda iz kuce.

430
00:29:10,196 --> 00:29:11,489
Javicemo joj se.

431
00:29:11,989 --> 00:29:13,032
Zasto?

432
00:29:13,449 --> 00:29:16,618
Nije lepo da odemo
a da se ne javimo,

433
00:29:16,785 --> 00:29:18,202
ipak ti je ona sestra.

434
00:29:18,369 --> 00:29:20,579
Sta ti je sad odjednom?

435
00:29:20,955 --> 00:29:22,790
To je pitanje vaspitanja, mama.

436
00:29:23,457 --> 00:29:26,292
Ma dacu ja i tebi i tvojoj tetki.

437
00:29:26,459 --> 00:29:27,794
Kako si prosta!

438
00:29:33,256 --> 00:29:34,716
Otkud ti RAIMUNDA?

439
00:29:35,300 --> 00:29:36,718
Rucak za troje.

440
00:29:36,884 --> 00:29:41,221
I sta sad da radim sa njim u kuci,
tako nervozim, celo leto.

441
00:29:41,388 --> 00:29:43,056
Sto si smorena RAIMUNDA?

442
00:29:43,223 --> 00:29:45,600
Sta se dernjas?
Svakim danom si sve gluvlja!

443
00:29:45,767 --> 00:29:46,642
Jesam, gluva sam!

444
00:29:46,809 --> 00:29:50,646
Gluva ko top!
Dosli smo, taman da mi skratis malo kosu.

445
00:29:50,979 --> 00:29:53,440
Zasto me nisi nazvala,
imam musteriju.

446
00:29:55,275 --> 00:29:58,902
Ne brini, ne zuri mi se.
A i moramo da razgovaramo.

447
00:29:59,069 --> 00:30:00,279
O cemu?

448
00:30:00,445 --> 00:30:02,322
O tetkinoj kuci.

449
00:30:02,489 --> 00:30:04,157
Jel mogu da idem da gledam
TV?

450
00:30:04,324 --> 00:30:05,366
Idi.

451
00:30:06,409 --> 00:30:09,286
Moramo da vidimo sta cemo,
i da sredimo papire.

452
00:30:11,079 --> 00:30:11,788
Bako.

453
00:30:12,622 --> 00:30:13,748
Ovde sam.

454
00:30:13,915 --> 00:30:15,833
Nemoj da galamis,
tu mi je mama.

455
00:30:16,000 --> 00:30:17,459
Cula sam je.

456
00:30:23,089 --> 00:30:24,549
Sole,
gde je Ruskinja?

457
00:30:25,007 --> 00:30:26,091
Koja sad Ruskinja?

458
00:30:26,258 --> 00:30:28,051
Ona koja mi pomaze.

459
00:30:28,218 --> 00:30:31,513
Pricala sam joj kako su Borhu
isterali sa posla

460
00:30:31,679 --> 00:30:34,682
a ona se prepala ko zec,

461
00:30:34,849 --> 00:30:38,226
i ostavila me da pricam sama sa sobom.

462
00:30:38,435 --> 00:30:39,769
Morala je da izadje.

463
00:30:39,894 --> 00:30:42,397
Nije izasla,
nego istrcala.

464
00:30:42,688 --> 00:30:44,356
Ja cu da ti operem kosu.

465
00:30:44,523 --> 00:30:46,567
Ona je malo klaustrofobicna

466
00:30:46,692 --> 00:30:49,110
pa s vremena na vreme mora da
izadje napolje.

467
00:30:49,277 --> 00:30:51,321
Pa kako ti onda pomaze!
Jel je placas?

468
00:30:51,738 --> 00:30:53,697
Ne, imamo dogovor.

469
00:30:54,490 --> 00:30:57,242
Ovde jede i spava,
dala sam joj i maminu odecu.

470
00:30:57,409 --> 00:31:00,078
Ne svidja mi se sto dovlacis
kuci ljude koje ne poznajes.

471
00:31:00,245 --> 00:31:03,455
To smo joj i mi rekli,
ne mozes svima da verujes.

472
00:31:03,622 --> 00:31:06,917
Da vidis ti Ruskinju, ne mozes da zamislis
kako zivi ovde, kao kraljica.

473
00:31:07,083 --> 00:31:09,502
Sta je sa Pakom?
Kako je bilo sinoc?

474
00:31:09,669 --> 00:31:12,046
Lose. Svratio je samo po
garderobu.

475
00:31:12,713 --> 00:31:15,882
Mislim da zivi sa nekom,
ali ne znam gde, ni ne zanima me.

476
00:31:17,008 --> 00:31:19,260
Zasto mi nisi rekla da si
primila Ruskinju?

477
00:31:20,386 --> 00:31:21,929
Nemam pojma,
mora da sam zaboravila.

478
00:31:30,644 --> 00:31:33,272
Vidi,
pa to je Agustina!

479
00:31:35,732 --> 00:31:37,650
Dobro nam dosla, Agustina.

480
00:31:37,900 --> 00:31:38,943
Dobar dan.

481
00:31:39,110 --> 00:31:43,613
Od tvoje sestre smo saznali da vas je
vasa majka ostavila. Jel tako?

482
00:31:43,780 --> 00:31:47,658
Da. Ona je bila... hipik.

483
00:31:49,243 --> 00:31:50,703
To je Agustina!

484
00:31:50,869 --> 00:31:52,120
I nikada se nije udavala.

485
00:31:52,954 --> 00:31:55,081
Znaci, upraznjavala je slobodnu
ljubav.

486
00:31:55,248 --> 00:31:56,916
Vasa majka je imala
jednu prijateljicu

487
00:31:57,041 --> 00:32:00,502
koja je umrla isti dan kada je vasa majka
nestala. Jel tako?

488
00:32:00,669 --> 00:32:01,503
Da.

489
00:32:02,421 --> 00:32:03,755
Kako je umrla ta njena prijateljica?

490
00:32:04,631 --> 00:32:05,840
U pozaru.

491
00:32:06,007 --> 00:32:08,384
U mom selu su cesti
pozari,

492
00:32:08,634 --> 00:32:10,260
zbog vetra.

493
00:32:10,427 --> 00:32:11,720
Agustinino selo se

494
00:32:11,887 --> 00:32:14,847
nalazi na predivnoj lokaciji
Alcanfor de las Infantas,

495
00:32:15,014 --> 00:32:17,099
koje po statistikama,

496
00:32:17,266 --> 00:32:19,810
ima najvise ludih ljudi
po glavi stanovnika.

497
00:32:19,977 --> 00:32:23,563
Agustina,da ne mislis mozda da je tvoja
majka dozivela neko nervno rastrojstvo?

498
00:32:24,564 --> 00:32:25,773
Ne, ne, ne, ne.

499
00:32:26,899 --> 00:32:29,026
Moja majka,
kad joj je bilo lose,

500
00:32:29,192 --> 00:32:31,945
kao u doba hipi pokreta,
takodje je odlazila...

501
00:32:32,820 --> 00:32:35,114
Sve dok jednog dana nije otisla
i nikada se nije vratila.

502
00:32:35,281 --> 00:32:38,033
Da, od tada ima skoro 4
godine.

503
00:32:38,909 --> 00:32:42,036
A njena prijateljica? Veoma nas
zanima ta prijateljica koja je umrla

504
00:32:42,203 --> 00:32:45,581
istog dana kad je tvoja majka nestala.
Ispricaj nam.

505
00:32:46,832 --> 00:32:47,791
Sta?

506
00:32:48,333 --> 00:32:52,295
Da. Pricamo o gospodji koja
je umrla u pozaru.

507
00:32:52,462 --> 00:32:54,213
Znas sta su tracevi...

508
00:32:54,380 --> 00:32:56,048
Ja ne verujem u traceve.

509
00:32:56,215 --> 00:32:59,384
Po prici nase rediteljke...

510
00:32:59,551 --> 00:33:01,386
Postoji veza izmedju stradalih u pozaru

511
00:33:01,552 --> 00:33:05,931
i nestanka tvoje majke,
Jeste ili nije, Agustina?

512
00:33:08,183 --> 00:33:09,476
O tome...

513
00:33:12,144 --> 00:33:13,145
ne bih zelela da pricam.

514
00:33:13,687 --> 00:33:15,564
To su samo lazne sumnje.

515
00:33:16,023 --> 00:33:18,233
Da, ali ti si dosla ovamo

516
00:33:18,400 --> 00:33:21,110
da pricas o toj gospodji i svojoj
majci.

517
00:33:21,360 --> 00:33:22,987
Da, ali sam se predomislila.

518
00:33:24,988 --> 00:33:28,032
Sta ti je? Vidim da ti nije prijatno,
malo si nervozna.

519
00:33:29,367 --> 00:33:32,661
Zelela bih da mi objasnis
da li si ti ista ona Agustina

520
00:33:32,828 --> 00:33:35,122
koja je dosla ovde
da razgovaramo o

521
00:33:35,288 --> 00:33:37,165
teskoj bolesti koja ti je
dijagnostikovana? Jel tako?

522
00:33:37,957 --> 00:33:39,834
Agustina ima rak.

523
00:33:40,001 --> 00:33:41,502
Uh, uh, uh!

524
00:33:43,795 --> 00:33:45,380
Ti imas rak, Agustina.

525
00:33:45,797 --> 00:33:48,424
Ali ne budi nervozna,
jer si medju prijateljima.

526
00:33:48,591 --> 00:33:50,634
Dajte jedan veliki aplauz
za Agustinu.

527
00:33:57,890 --> 00:34:00,184
Agustina ima jednu zelju:

528
00:34:00,517 --> 00:34:02,477
a to je da ide u Hjuston na lecenje.

529
00:34:02,936 --> 00:34:05,939
Ali ako zelis da ides u Hjuston,
moras jasno da pricas.

530
00:34:06,397 --> 00:34:09,483
Podsecam te da si obecala
da ces saradjivati.

531
00:34:12,110 --> 00:34:13,278
Agustina!

532
00:34:14,571 --> 00:34:15,822
Agustina!

533
00:34:18,866 --> 00:34:20,033
Ah!

534
00:34:35,921 --> 00:34:38,048
Agustina me je posetila
u restoranu.

535
00:34:38,215 --> 00:34:39,299
Aha, i?

536
00:34:39,549 --> 00:34:41,760
Ona tvrdi da ce
nam se mama pojaviti.

537
00:34:41,926 --> 00:34:43,886
I hoce da je pitamo za
njenu majku.

538
00:34:44,887 --> 00:34:47,139
Takodje mi je rekla,
da kada je nestala,

539
00:34:47,306 --> 00:34:49,766
njena majka je bila u vezi
sa tatom.

540
00:34:55,646 --> 00:34:57,898
Da ne znas ti nesto, slucajno, o tome?

541
00:34:58,774 --> 00:34:59,774
Ne.

542
00:35:01,693 --> 00:35:04,487
Dobro,
mama mi je rekla da je kasnije...

543
00:35:07,114 --> 00:35:08,448
Sta je kasnije?

544
00:35:08,615 --> 00:35:11,075
Da je kasnije saznala.

545
00:35:14,578 --> 00:35:15,871
Sole, pogledaj me.

546
00:35:18,832 --> 00:35:21,584
Ima tu neceg vise sto ne znam
a trebalo bi da znam?

547
00:35:22,251 --> 00:35:23,586
Mnogo.

548
00:35:24,837 --> 00:35:26,546
Ali ako ti kazem

549
00:35:26,713 --> 00:35:29,132
nadrkaces se,
ili mi neces verovati.

550
00:35:29,674 --> 00:35:32,551
Obecavam da cu ti verovati
i da se necu nardkati.

551
00:35:33,969 --> 00:35:36,346
Mama je nastavila da se
pojavljuje.

552
00:35:38,515 --> 00:35:39,682
Kome?

553
00:35:39,849 --> 00:35:40,766
Sedi.

554
00:35:46,604 --> 00:35:49,023
Bila je kod tetka Paule kad
je umrla.

555
00:35:49,732 --> 00:35:52,026
Videla je Agustinu
i otvorila je vrata

556
00:35:52,192 --> 00:35:54,152
Da bi je ona pronasla mrtvu.

557
00:35:54,319 --> 00:35:57,280
Ona je ta koja je davala tetki pare
da joj Agustina donosi hleb.

558
00:35:57,447 --> 00:35:58,948
i platila je sahranu.

559
00:35:59,073 --> 00:36:00,699
Ti si sve to uradila, bako?

560
00:36:00,866 --> 00:36:01,825
Da.

561
00:36:02,993 --> 00:36:05,161
Ko ti je sve to napricao?
Agustina?

562
00:36:06,704 --> 00:36:08,289
Vidis da mi ne verujes?

563
00:36:10,207 --> 00:36:12,125
Sole, Agustina je luda!

564
00:36:13,210 --> 00:36:14,919
Poslednji put kad smo isli
kod tetke,

565
00:36:15,086 --> 00:36:17,672
sama si rekla,
da je prosto nemoguce

566
00:36:17,838 --> 00:36:21,383
da tetka zivi sama,
izlapela i poluslepa.

567
00:36:21,675 --> 00:36:22,676
Ne secas se?

568
00:36:23,385 --> 00:36:25,470
Da, ali sta hoces time da kazes?

569
00:36:26,345 --> 00:36:28,222
Da tetka nije bila sama.

570
00:36:29,473 --> 00:36:31,433
Sta mislis ko je pravio sve
one kolace

571
00:36:31,600 --> 00:36:34,894
i pakovao ih u zasebne
kutije, jedna sa tvojim, jedna sa mojim imenom?

572
00:36:35,061 --> 00:36:37,688
Sta mislis ko je uzeo lutke
i tetkine stvari

573
00:36:37,855 --> 00:36:40,315
pre nego sto je komsiluk
razgrabio sve?

574
00:36:40,732 --> 00:36:42,359
Jel sada razumes?

575
00:36:46,529 --> 00:36:47,946
Jesi li je ti videla?

576
00:36:48,447 --> 00:36:49,406
Da.

577
00:36:54,118 --> 00:36:55,911
Da nije ona mozda...

578
00:36:56,245 --> 00:36:57,204
Ruskinja?

579
00:36:58,413 --> 00:36:59,456
Jeste.

580
00:37:01,332 --> 00:37:02,709
I gde je ona?

581
00:37:05,544 --> 00:37:06,462
Tu je.

582
00:37:34,943 --> 00:37:35,944
Mama.

583
00:37:36,737 --> 00:37:38,238
Pa sta radis tu?

584
00:38:00,214 --> 00:38:02,257
Pa ti nisi mrtva?

585
00:38:03,258 --> 00:38:05,385
Dosla sam da te
molim za oprostaj.

586
00:38:07,220 --> 00:38:09,222
Ja ne znam nista, kceri moja.

587
00:38:10,264 --> 00:38:11,974
Nisam mogla ni da zamislim.

588
00:38:16,394 --> 00:38:17,979
Hajdemo, Paula.

589
00:38:21,482 --> 00:38:22,524
Raimunda!

590
00:38:32,824 --> 00:38:34,242
Dete moje!

591
00:38:35,201 --> 00:38:36,452
Dete moje!

592
00:38:37,870 --> 00:38:39,204
Najgore je proslo.

593
00:38:40,164 --> 00:38:41,540
Videla me je,

594
00:38:41,998 --> 00:38:43,625
I nije me odbacila, zar ne?

595
00:38:44,083 --> 00:38:44,959
Ne.

596
00:38:47,003 --> 00:38:49,880
Jel istina da si
dosla da trazis oprostaj?

597
00:38:50,255 --> 00:38:52,465
I da budem sa tobom.

598
00:38:54,050 --> 00:38:56,635
Hoces li mi jednog dana objasniti
sta se tu desilo?

599
00:38:56,761 --> 00:39:00,597
Hocu, i nadam se
da ces me razumeti, Sole.

600
00:39:01,765 --> 00:39:03,558
i da ces mi i ti oprostiti.

601
00:39:14,775 --> 00:39:15,901
Mama...

602
00:39:20,196 --> 00:39:21,114
Uzmi.

603
00:39:29,954 --> 00:39:31,664
Moram da pricam sa njom.

604
00:39:32,498 --> 00:39:34,291
Hajde da se vratimo?

605
00:39:37,210 --> 00:39:38,378
Sada?

606
00:39:38,962 --> 00:39:40,004
Naravno.

607
00:40:05,942 --> 00:40:08,319
Toliko sam puta sanjala ovo.

608
00:40:08,486 --> 00:40:09,445
I ja isto.

609
00:40:11,530 --> 00:40:13,198
Ne znam odakle da pocnem.

610
00:40:14,408 --> 00:40:17,410
Stvarno nisi duh?
Stvarno nisi mrtva?

611
00:40:17,994 --> 00:40:19,203
Ne, kceri, nisam.

612
00:40:20,830 --> 00:40:22,206
Moras da mi dokazes.

613
00:40:22,998 --> 00:40:24,583
Da sam umrla,

614
00:40:24,749 --> 00:40:26,668
vratila bih se
da te molim za oprostaj

615
00:40:26,834 --> 00:40:29,503
sto nisam obracala
paznju na ono sto ti se desilo.

616
00:40:30,296 --> 00:40:31,588
Bila sam slepa.

617
00:40:32,673 --> 00:40:34,758
Saznala sam istog dana
kad je izbio pozar.

618
00:40:36,092 --> 00:40:37,969
Jel tacno da si otisla od oca?

619
00:40:38,302 --> 00:40:39,303
Jeste.

620
00:40:40,095 --> 00:40:42,014
Nisam mogla da zivim sa
kurvarom.

621
00:40:43,223 --> 00:40:44,849
Posle pozara,

622
00:40:45,308 --> 00:40:48,060
ti si zvala i pricala sa tetkom.

623
00:40:48,853 --> 00:40:51,146
Kao i uvek,
nisi pitala za mene,

624
00:40:51,521 --> 00:40:54,816
to me je povredilo i rekla
sam tvojoj tetki kako si bezosecajna.

625
00:40:55,900 --> 00:40:57,693
I posto sam nastavila da
prosipam uvrede,

626
00:40:58,819 --> 00:40:59,903
tetka je

627
00:41:00,779 --> 00:41:02,322
stala u tvoju odbranu,

628
00:41:03,948 --> 00:41:05,825
i sve mi rekla.

629
00:41:11,288 --> 00:41:13,498
Da te je otac zlostavljao,

630
00:41:14,874 --> 00:41:16,750
i da si zatrudnela...

631
00:41:17,668 --> 00:41:18,794
i da je Paula

632
00:41:19,795 --> 00:41:21,379
tvoja cerka...

633
00:41:21,671 --> 00:41:23,506
i tvoja sestra ujednom.

634
00:41:25,132 --> 00:41:26,717
Nisam mogla da verujem.

635
00:41:27,759 --> 00:41:31,262
Kako je nesto tako moglo da se
desi pred mojim ocima,

636
00:41:31,429 --> 00:41:33,014
a da to ne primetim?

637
00:41:35,182 --> 00:41:37,643
Tada sam sve shvatila.

638
00:41:39,185 --> 00:41:41,104
Shvatila sam tvoju cutljivost,

639
00:41:41,354 --> 00:41:43,439
i tvoju povucenost.

640
00:41:44,023 --> 00:41:47,275
Shvatila sam, da je tvoj otac otisao
da radi u Venecuelu,

641
00:41:48,235 --> 00:41:51,362
jer nije mogao
da podnese sramotu koju je pocinio.

642
00:41:52,571 --> 00:41:53,906
Shvatila sam i da,

643
00:41:54,573 --> 00:41:56,658
posto si se udala za Paka,

644
00:41:57,200 --> 00:41:58,451
i otisla u Madrid

645
00:41:59,410 --> 00:42:01,787
nisi zelela da znas nista
o nama.

646
00:42:01,954 --> 00:42:04,748
Mrzela sam te zato
sto te je bilo briga za sve, mama.

647
00:42:05,499 --> 00:42:07,751
Potpuno si u pravu, kceri moja.

648
00:42:08,751 --> 00:42:10,211
Kad sam saznala,

649
00:42:10,711 --> 00:42:12,546
nisi ni svesna kako sam reagovala!

650
00:42:14,006 --> 00:42:16,883
Otisla sam do kolibe
da bih se uverila.

651
00:42:17,050 --> 00:42:20,052
I zatekla sam ga u krevetu
sa Agustininom majkom,

652
00:42:20,219 --> 00:42:21,929
skroz iscrpljeni!

653
00:42:22,096 --> 00:42:23,472
Nisu me videli.

654
00:42:24,598 --> 00:42:26,558
Podmetnula sam pozar.

655
00:42:27,141 --> 00:42:28,893
Bilo je jako vetrovito,

656
00:42:29,101 --> 00:42:32,229
i za kratko vreme
vatra je sve unistila.

657
00:42:33,021 --> 00:42:35,106
Nisu imali vremena ni
da se probude.

658
00:42:36,774 --> 00:42:38,985
Pepeo koji je sahranjen na
tvom mestu

659
00:42:39,318 --> 00:42:41,570
je od Agustinine majke?

660
00:42:42,404 --> 00:42:43,447
Da.

661
00:42:47,575 --> 00:42:48,909
Nakon toga,

662
00:42:49,743 --> 00:42:52,788
nekoliko dana sam lutala
po polju.

663
00:42:53,580 --> 00:42:54,914
Krila se,

664
00:42:55,456 --> 00:42:56,874
kao neka zivotinja.

665
00:42:58,042 --> 00:42:59,793
Mislila sam da se prijavim,

666
00:43:00,502 --> 00:43:01,628
ali sam

667
00:43:01,878 --> 00:43:04,631
otisla do tetka Paule da
je vidim.

668
00:43:05,673 --> 00:43:07,675
A njoj je bilo tako lose...

669
00:43:08,550 --> 00:43:10,302
Kada me je videla,

670
00:43:10,761 --> 00:43:12,804
nije se nimalo zacudila.

671
00:43:13,471 --> 00:43:16,349
Dosla sam do njene kuce,

672
00:43:17,725 --> 00:43:20,644
i ona me je primila
kao da se nista nije desilo.

673
00:43:22,812 --> 00:43:25,731
Tragedija koju je dozivela
oduzela joj je i to malo razuma sto je imala.

674
00:43:26,815 --> 00:43:28,775
Nisam mogla da
je ostavim samu,

675
00:43:29,609 --> 00:43:32,695
pa sam pocela da se
brinem o njoj

676
00:43:33,780 --> 00:43:35,197
dok nije umrla.

677
00:43:39,326 --> 00:43:41,995
Mama, u selu misle da si
ti duh.

678
00:43:42,412 --> 00:43:45,206
Dobro je sto su takva
sela sujeverna.

679
00:43:45,497 --> 00:43:48,667
Meni je bilo lakse
da nastavim po njihovom

680
00:43:48,834 --> 00:43:50,418
nego da im ispricam istinu.

681
00:43:50,960 --> 00:43:53,087
Mislila sam da ce me provaliti,

682
00:43:53,462 --> 00:43:56,673
nisam mogla da verujem
da niko nije istrazivao

683
00:43:56,840 --> 00:43:58,300
i kaznio me,

684
00:43:59,009 --> 00:44:01,636
mada svo to vreme

685
00:44:02,178 --> 00:44:04,930
kunem ti se, zivela sam kao
u pravom cistilistu.

686
00:44:09,684 --> 00:44:11,727
Ko bi rekao.

687
00:44:31,035 --> 00:44:33,036
Uskoro stizemo u selo.

688
00:44:33,203 --> 00:44:34,788
Necemo stici po danu.

689
00:44:34,955 --> 00:44:39,458
Zasto ne prodjemo pored reke?
Znas od kad je nisam videla...

690
00:44:39,625 --> 00:44:41,752
Nema je vise, mama.
Presusila je.

691
00:44:41,919 --> 00:44:43,253
Odakle znas?

692
00:44:44,421 --> 00:44:48,841
Bila je susa u celoj Spaniji, Sole,
zar nisi cula?

693
00:45:07,565 --> 00:45:10,859
Ovde smo cesto dolazili na izlet.
Jel se secas, Raimunda?

694
00:45:11,610 --> 00:45:12,569
Secam se.

695
00:45:13,403 --> 00:45:15,488
Samo sto je tada bilo
vise vode.

696
00:45:15,655 --> 00:45:17,281
Meni su rekli da je presusila.

697
00:45:17,865 --> 00:45:19,158
Hocemo da jedemo nesto?

698
00:45:19,783 --> 00:45:20,951
Ja necu.

699
00:45:21,451 --> 00:45:23,036
Ja cu da uzmem jednu krofnu.

700
00:45:23,203 --> 00:45:24,162
I ja cu.

701
00:45:34,295 --> 00:45:36,422
Ovo je bilo omiljeno
mesto tvoga oca.

702
00:45:37,631 --> 00:45:38,882
Paka?

703
00:45:39,508 --> 00:45:40,258
Da.

704
00:45:42,343 --> 00:45:44,553
To je jedino sto mu je
nedostajalo:

705
00:45:44,929 --> 00:45:45,888
reka!

706
00:46:05,779 --> 00:46:07,781
Drago mi je sto
pociva ovde.

707
00:46:19,958 --> 00:46:21,917
Vidi, pa nema nikoga.

708
00:46:36,763 --> 00:46:38,598
Eh, da je Paula ziva,

709
00:46:39,182 --> 00:46:40,683
i da nas sad vidi,

710
00:46:41,392 --> 00:46:42,976
sve zajedno...

711
00:46:43,477 --> 00:46:45,020
kako bi joj bilo drago!

712
00:46:52,192 --> 00:46:54,945
Kceri,
jesi li ti uvek imala tolike grudi?

713
00:46:55,195 --> 00:46:57,030
Da, mama, jos od malena.

714
00:46:57,155 --> 00:46:59,990
Stvarno...Secam te se sa
manjim grudima.

715
00:47:00,950 --> 00:47:02,701
Nisi valjda nesto radila sa njima?

716
00:47:02,993 --> 00:47:05,036
Sta da radim? Na sta mislis, mama?

717
00:47:05,328 --> 00:47:06,287
Dobro, dobro.

718
00:47:06,537 --> 00:47:08,539
Bako, jel ti vozis
sobni bicikl?

719
00:47:08,706 --> 00:47:10,291
Da, pola sata svaki dan.

720
00:47:10,457 --> 00:47:12,793
Dobro je za pritisak
i za srce.

721
00:47:12,959 --> 00:47:15,670
I sta je tetka Paula rekla,
kad je videla?

722
00:47:15,837 --> 00:47:17,505
Upisala se od smeha.

723
00:47:20,757 --> 00:47:21,508
Vidimo se posle.

724
00:47:25,178 --> 00:47:26,345
Jel to tetka Paula?

725
00:47:26,721 --> 00:47:27,847
Sole, ne lupaj.

726
00:47:29,056 --> 00:47:30,224
Idem da vidim ko je.

727
00:47:31,183 --> 00:47:33,518
Sklonite mamin tanjir.

728
00:47:39,273 --> 00:47:40,107
Ko je?

729
00:47:40,273 --> 00:47:41,441
Ja sam, Agustina.

730
00:47:45,194 --> 00:47:47,238
Veceramo, samo sto smo stigli.

731
00:47:47,404 --> 00:47:48,906
Izvinite sto vas uznemiravam.

732
00:47:49,948 --> 00:47:51,574
Udji, nemoj da stojis tu.

733
00:47:51,991 --> 00:47:53,159
Hvala.

734
00:47:58,038 --> 00:47:59,372
Dobro vece.

735
00:47:59,748 --> 00:48:00,665
Dobro vece.

736
00:48:00,832 --> 00:48:02,041
Sedi, zeno.

737
00:48:02,208 --> 00:48:03,167
Hvala.

738
00:48:10,048 --> 00:48:12,800
Dosla sam da vam se izvinim
zbog one emisije na TV-u.

739
00:48:13,426 --> 00:48:16,261
Nisi trebala da ides.
Nije dobro ispalo.

740
00:48:16,470 --> 00:48:17,429
Znam.

741
00:48:17,637 --> 00:48:18,972
Nije neko opravdanje,

742
00:48:19,139 --> 00:48:21,349
ponudili su mi da
idem u Hjuston,

743
00:48:21,516 --> 00:48:23,434
jer se tamo sve leci,

744
00:48:24,059 --> 00:48:25,644
ali nisam ja vredna toga.

745
00:48:25,978 --> 00:48:29,147
Vise volim da umrem sama
u svojoj kuci mirna...

746
00:48:29,480 --> 00:48:31,357
i da mogu da vas pogledam u oci.

747
00:48:33,442 --> 00:48:34,943
Mama, ja sam zavrsila,
mogu li?

748
00:48:35,527 --> 00:48:36,486
Da, da, idi.

749
00:48:38,738 --> 00:48:39,781
Hoces da veceras?

750
00:48:39,947 --> 00:48:41,073
Ne, ne, hvala.

751
00:48:41,532 --> 00:48:43,492
Cula sam da si dosla
da prodas kucu.

752
00:48:43,659 --> 00:48:44,284
Da.

753
00:48:44,785 --> 00:48:47,203
Jos uvek razmisljamo, medjutim...

754
00:48:48,204 --> 00:48:50,373
ima toliko uspomena,
da ne znam sta da radim.

755
00:48:51,540 --> 00:48:53,333
Dobro, idem ja.

756
00:48:54,209 --> 00:48:56,211
Gde ces, zeno?
Gde zuris?

757
00:48:56,795 --> 00:49:00,006
Moram da idem da primim injekciju.

758
00:49:00,172 --> 00:49:03,467
U Madridu su mi rekli da
sama sebi dajem injekcije,

759
00:49:03,634 --> 00:49:05,385
ali ja ne znam da
dam sama sebi.

760
00:49:05,719 --> 00:49:09,180
Za tvoju sestru nema opravdanja!
Ostavila te je da zivis sama, sa svom tom bolescu.

761
00:49:09,347 --> 00:49:10,889
Ne pominji mi moju sestru.

762
00:49:11,765 --> 00:49:14,267
Kad na TV-u nisam rekla ono sto je
ona zelela da kazem

763
00:49:14,434 --> 00:49:16,019
sad ne prica sa mnom.

764
00:49:16,227 --> 00:49:19,605
Mnogo je ljuta na mene.
Ali ja sam vise ljuta na nju.

765
00:49:20,189 --> 00:49:21,482
Stvarno nemas razloga da budes ljuta.

766
00:49:21,648 --> 00:49:22,983
Bas vam zavidim!

767
00:49:24,609 --> 00:49:26,361
Tako ste slozne...

768
00:49:45,877 --> 00:49:47,169
Irene!

769
00:49:49,004 --> 00:49:50,672
Kako sam zelela da te vidim!

770
00:49:50,922 --> 00:49:52,173
Pa evo me.

771
00:49:53,132 --> 00:49:54,467
Videla sam tvoje...

772
00:49:55,092 --> 00:49:57,678
i zamislila kroz koju samocu
prolazis.

773
00:49:58,011 --> 00:49:59,012
Veliku samocu.

774
00:50:02,974 --> 00:50:05,351
Nadala sam se i tvojoj sestri Pauli...

775
00:50:05,518 --> 00:50:07,936
Tu sam ja da ti
pomognem ako nesto krene naopako.

776
00:50:08,103 --> 00:50:09,896
Nemoj da ostavljas vrata
otvorena.

777
00:50:10,355 --> 00:50:12,523
Ne brini,
ja sam ih zatvorila.

778
00:50:12,857 --> 00:50:14,400
Jesi li isla da primis
injekciju?

779
00:50:14,567 --> 00:50:16,819
Ne, mnogo sam umorna.
Sutra cu.

780
00:50:17,110 --> 00:50:19,738
Sutra ces umirati od bolova.

781
00:50:19,904 --> 00:50:22,532
Jel imas lek i spric i iglu
da ti dam injekciju?

782
00:50:22,698 --> 00:50:24,241
Imam, kupila sam sve u
Madridu.

783
00:50:24,408 --> 00:50:26,868
Odlicno,
dacu ti ja injekciju.

784
00:50:32,373 --> 00:50:34,416
Ja spavam u ovom krevetu.

785
00:50:35,709 --> 00:50:37,586
Ovde je spavala moja
majka.

786
00:50:38,712 --> 00:50:41,964
I u istom ovom krevetu smo
ispratili tvoju sestru Paulu.

787
00:50:42,423 --> 00:50:43,924
Znam, Agustina.

788
00:50:44,550 --> 00:50:46,301
I veoma sam ti zahvalna.

789
00:50:50,513 --> 00:50:53,057
Moramo da
razgovaramo, Irene.

790
00:50:53,474 --> 00:50:55,308
O cemu god hoces,

791
00:50:55,934 --> 00:50:58,019
samo nikom ni reci da
si me videla.

792
00:50:58,228 --> 00:51:00,396
Ne brini.

793
00:51:01,105 --> 00:51:05,192
Ah, hvala ti sto nisi pricala o meni
na televiziji.

794
00:51:06,401 --> 00:51:08,486
To su nase stvari.

795
00:51:09,362 --> 00:51:10,696
A drugo,

796
00:51:10,988 --> 00:51:13,156
koga se pa ticu nase stvari.

797
00:52:18,252 --> 00:52:20,212
Mama! Ja sam,
otvori!

798
00:52:22,630 --> 00:52:24,924
Raimunda,
sta ces ti ovde? Udji.

799
00:52:26,508 --> 00:52:27,926
Nedostajala si mi.

800
00:52:28,093 --> 00:52:29,553
Ostaces ovde?

801
00:52:29,719 --> 00:52:31,304
Da. Do kraja.

802
00:52:31,971 --> 00:52:33,556
Agustini je mnogo lose.

803
00:52:33,973 --> 00:52:35,849
Nakon svega sto sam uradila
njenoj majci,

804
00:52:36,016 --> 00:52:38,476
sta drugo mogu,
osim da se brinem o njoj dok ne umre,zar ne?

805
00:52:38,643 --> 00:52:41,938
Da. Mama, imam mnogo
toga da te pitam.

806
00:52:42,104 --> 00:52:44,440
Nisam ti nista rekla o Paku.
Najveci problem koji imam.

807
00:52:44,607 --> 00:52:47,692
Hocu sve da mi ispricas,
ali idi sada.

808
00:52:47,859 --> 00:52:51,112
Vidjacemo se svaki dan.
Bitno je da se razumemo.

809
00:52:51,404 --> 00:52:52,446
Da.

810
00:52:55,073 --> 00:52:56,658
Trebas mi, mama.

811
00:52:59,285 --> 00:53:02,246
Ne znam kako sam
zivela sve ove godine bez tebe.

812
00:53:02,621 --> 00:53:04,373
Ne govori mi to, Raimunda,

813
00:53:04,998 --> 00:53:06,416
rasplakacu se.

814
00:53:07,125 --> 00:53:09,377
A duhovi ne placu!

